{
  "Changes": [
    {
      "LogName": "Hogwarts Acceptance Letter Mail Data",
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Mail",
      "Entries": {
        "{{ModId}}_HogwartsLetterAcceptance": "HOGWARTS SCHOOL of WITCHCRAFT and WIZARDRY^         Headmistress: Minerva McGonagall^          (Order of Merlin, First Class)^^Dear ${Mr^Ms}$ @,^    We are pleased to inform you that you have successfully passed your first year at Hogwarts. Enclosed is your report and a list of necessary books and equipment for the upcoming year. Place the emblem attached to the letter at one of the designated spots for an owl to pick up.^^*Guild for brave adventurers^*Shop selling seeds and saplings^*Museum containing books^*Forest that leads to a dark entrance^^We look forward to your owl's reply,^Filius Flitwick^Deputy Headmaster^COURSE BOOKS^All students should have a copy of each of the following:^^Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them^by Newt Scamander^^The Monster Book of Monsters^by Edwardus Lima^^OTHER EQUIPMENT^1 wand^1 cauldron^1 telescope^1 dark detector with eyes^Students may also bring, if they desire, a pet.^^Yours sincerely,^Lucinda Thomsonicle-Pocus^Chief Attendant of Witchcraft Provisions%item id (O){{ModId}}_HogwartsEmblem 1 %%[#]A Letter From Hogwarts",
        "{{ModId}}_Wizard": "HOGWARTS SCHOOL of WITCHCRAFT and WIZARDRY^         Headmistress: Minerva McGonagall^          (Order of Merlin, First Class)^^Dear ${Mr^Ms}$ @,^    We have received your owl. To reach Hogsmeade Station, please use one of the following methods:^*Wizard's Tower Floo Flame^*Floo Flame using a furniture^Sincerely,^Filius Flitwick^Deputy Headmaster[#]Locations To Use Floo Flame"
      }
    },
    {
      "LogName": "Hogwarts Letter Trigger Actions Mail",
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/TriggerActions",
      "Entries": {
        "{{ModId}}_HogwartsLetterAcceptanceAddMail": {
          "Id": "{{ModId}}_HogwartsLetterAcceptanceAddMail",
          "Trigger": "DayStarted",
          "Condition": "!PLAYER_HAS_MAIL Any {{ModId}}_HogwartsLetterAcceptance received, {{HasMod |contains= aedenthorn.DynamicMapTilesExtended}}, !{{HasFlag |contains= {{ModId}}_Hufflepuff, {{ModId}}_Gryffindor, {{ModId}}_Slytherin, {{ModId}}_Ravenclaw}}",
          "Action": "AddMail all {{ModId}}_HogwartsLetterAcceptance now",
          "MarkActionApplied": false
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "LogName": "Hogwarts Emblem Object",
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Objects",
      "Entries": {
        "{{ModId}}_HogwartsEmblem": {
          "Name": "Hogwarts Emblem",
          "DisplayName": "Hogwarts Emblem",
